			{
				"id": "ep-s2-06",
				"slug": "the-end-of-the-feed",
				"status": "published",
				"data": {
					"title": "The end of the feed",
					"description": "A wide-ranging conversation with Priya Raman on what replaces the infinite scroll — and why the next decade of interfaces won't look like a timeline.",
					"cover_image": {
						"$media": {
							"url": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1611532736597-de2d4265fba3?w=1200&h=1200&fit=crop",
							"alt": "Neon abstract podcast cover",
							"filename": "ep-s2-06.jpg"
						}
					},
					"audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/testmp3testfile/mpthreetest.mp3",
					"duration": "58:24",
					"duration_seconds": 3504,
					"episode_number": 24,
					"published_at": "2026-03-27T09:00:00.000Z",
					"spotify_url": "https://open.spotify.com/episode/xxx",
					"apple_url": "https://podcasts.apple.com/episode/xxx",
					"youtube_url": "https://youtube.com/watch?v=xxx",
					"show_notes": [
						{ "_type": "block", "style": "normal", "children": [{ "_type": "span", "text": "Priya joins Maya and Rafael to break down why she thinks the feed is a dead-end paradigm, and what a post-scroll interface actually looks like." }] },
						{ "_type": "block", "style": "h2", "children": [{ "_type": "span", "text": "00:00" }] },
						{ "_type": "block", "style": "normal", "children": [{ "_type": "span", "text": "Cold open and introductions" }] },
						{ "_type": "block", "style": "h2", "children": [{ "_type": "span", "text": "04:12" }] },
						{ "_type": "block", "style": "normal", "children": [{ "_type": "span", "text": "How Lumen got started and the first prototype Priya built in a weekend" }] },
						{ "_type": "block", "style": "h2", "children": [{ "_type": "span", "text": "12:45" }] },
						{ "_type": "block", "style": "normal", "children": [{ "_type": "span", "text": "Why the infinite feed is not a user preference but a business constraint" }] },
						{ "_type": "block", "style": "h2", "children": [{ "_type": "span", "text": "24:30" }] },
						{ "_type": "block", "style": "normal", "children": [{ "_type": "span", "text": "Generative canvas: demoing a real product that replaces the timeline" }] },
						{ "_type": "block", "style": "h2", "children": [{ "_type": "span", "text": "38:02" }] },
						{ "_type": "block", "style": "normal", "children": [{ "_type": "span", "text": "What happens to discovery without ranked feeds?" }] },
						{ "_type": "block", "style": "h2", "children": [{ "_type": "span", "text": "49:15" }] },
						{ "_type": "block", "style": "normal", "children": [{ "_type": "span", "text": "The business model problem and why this is hard to fund" }] },
						{ "_type": "block", "style": "h3", "children": [{ "_type": "span", "text": "Resources mentioned" }] },
						{ "_type": "block", "listItem": "bullet", "children": [{ "_type": "span", "text": "Lumen's research paper on post-feed interfaces" }] },
						{ "_type": "block", "listItem": "bullet", "children": [{ "_type": "span", "text": "Priya's essay 'Against the timeline'" }] },
						{ "_type": "block", "listItem": "bullet", "children": [{ "_type": "span", "text": "Apple Vision Pro's spatial UI as a partial solution" }] }
					],
					"transcript": [
						{ "_type": "block", "style": "h3", "children": [{ "_type": "span", "text": "MAYA CHEN" }] },
						{ "_type": "block", "style": "normal", "children": [{ "_type": "span", "text": "Priya, thanks so much for being here. I want to start with a provocation from your last essay — you said the feed is over. What did you mean by that?" }] },
						{ "_type": "block", "style": "h3", "children": [{ "_type": "span", "text": "PRIYA RAMAN" }] },
						{ "_type": "block", "style": "normal", "children": [{ "_type": "span", "text": "Thanks for having me. I think the feed was a brilliant invention for a specific moment — when we had more content than attention and needed a ranking function to figure out what mattered. But that constraint is gone. Generative models can produce an interface tailored to you in real time. Why are we still scrolling a list someone else ordered?" }] },
						{ "_type": "block", "style": "h3", "children": [{ "_type": "span", "text": "RAFAEL ORTIZ" }] },
						{ "_type": "block", "style": "normal", "children": [{ "_type": "span", "text": "But ranking is also how ad inventory gets priced. You can't just hand-wave that away…" }] }
					]
				},
				"bylines": [{ "byline": "byline-signal-noise" }],
